        VideoFilePath       = {'', ''}        % [V3.19 (1)] worker媛 ?먯껜 VideoReader ?앹꽦??
        DragVelocity        = [0, 0]          % [V3.19 (2)] frames/sec (遺?? 諛⑺뼢)
