        % [V3.14 VirtualDub UI] Frame N / Total (HH:MM:SS.mmm) ?쇰꺼 媛깆떊
        % [V3.15 ??ぉ 5-1 / REFACTOR Step 0] ?쒓컙 ?щ㎎?낆쓣 util.TimeFormat?쇰줈 ?꾩엫
        function updateVdubFrameLabel(app, fIdx, frameNo)
            try
